  <h1>About Us</h1>
  <p>BW Construction is a close team of professionals with the experience and attention to detail needed to meet your unique project and individual family needs.  But it is our passion and sense of pride that brings the beauty, heart and fun to our work. Our focus is to make your remodel a smooth, enjoyable experience. Both our clients and BW crew are often sad to end their time together. <a href="/testimonials/">Hear what our satisfied clients have to say</a> about their BW experience!</p>
