    <h3>Donna Werner</h3>
    <h4>Owner, Office Manager &amp; Jane-of-all Trades</h4>
    <figure>
      <img src="/images/about/donna.jpg" alt="Donna Werner">
    </figure>
    <p>I am your initial contact for all BW communications and operations. From the first phone call through the last punch list item, my goal is to listen and pay attention to your details, to earn and keep your trust. Your calls will be answered, your concerns or questions promptly addressed, and your feedback solicited throughout your project.</p>
    <p>Having spent much of my time working as a teacher of special needs students, I understand the value and responsibility of community service.  We have built this in to our team and company philosophy, volunteering and supporting local agencies that include Boulder Valley School District, Boulder County Safehouse, Boulder Homeless Shelter and Boulder I Have A Dream Foundation.</p>
    <p>In addition to taking care of the BW family of employees and clients, I love to spend time with my own family, cooking, playing in our garden, practicing yoga, and helping new moms as a post partum doula.</p>
    <p>Please call me to learn more about BW Construction and find out how we can help you with your remodeling ideas.</p>
